00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:22.740
 And again, this is a reminder of the dry principle,

00:05:22.740 --> 00:05:25.260
 the don't repeat yourself principle.

00:05:25.260 --> 00:05:27.820
 Again, sometimes this dry principle gets us in trouble

00:05:27.820 --> 00:05:31.280
 because we, the idea is that some bit of logic

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:34.700
 is placed one place and reused as many places as possible,

00:05:34.700 --> 00:05:37.780
 'cause don't repeat yourself would probably,

00:05:37.780 --> 00:05:41.760
 as well described by Colin, reuse, reuse, reuse, reuse.

00:05:41.760 --> 00:05:44.500
 Do it once and then reuse it as many times as possible,

00:05:44.500 --> 00:05:46.500
 so that if you have to fix it and you got a bug in it,

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:48.400
 you don't have to find the 49 places

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:50.560
